file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Test
  version: 1.0.0

paths:
  /value:
    get:
      operationId: getValues
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/IdParam'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/NameParam'
      responses:
        200:
          description: Successful response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type:
                  string

components:
  parameters:
    IdParam:
      required: true
      name: id
      in: query
      schema:
        type: integer
        format: int64
    NameParam:
      required: false
      name: name
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
